data.description: Experience the epitome of modern living in this stunningly renovated townhome, strategically situated near Petroglyphs, convenient highway access, and vibrant dining and shopping destinations. Revel in the allure of a thoughtfully designed floorplan adorned with exquisite updates - envision sleek, 2021 gray cabinets, luxurious quartz countertops, and stylish tile throughout. Bask in the warmth of a central fireplace, casting the perfect ambiance. Every glance out the new (2021) windows reveals a private backyard oasis, complete with a chic lounging deck and towering walls for utmost seclusion. This residence is a captivating must-see, seamlessly blending contemporary elegance with prime location allure!
